### Fictional alien race in [Doctor Who](/Doctor_Who)

This article is about the fictional species. For the episode, see [Dalek (Doctor Who episode)](/Dalek_(Doctor_Who_episode)). For other uses, see [Dalek (disambiguation)](/Dalek_(disambiguation)).

• "Skaro" redirects here. For the island in Denmark, see [Skarø](/Skar%C3%B8). For the abandoned town in the Faeroes, see [Skarð](/Skar%C3%B0).

